ZH: 不管天气如何，我都要去慕尼黑旅行。
EN: No matter what the weather is like, I am going to Munich for vacation.

ZH: 不管你怎么想，我决定这样做。
EN: No matter what you think, I have decided to do it this way.

ZH: 不管多少困难，我们都要坚持下去。
EN: No matter how difficult it is, we must persevere.

ZH: 不管她气不气我，我都要告诉她真相。
EN: I don't care if she gets mad at me, I have to tell her the truth.

ZH: 不管是好是坏，这都是我的选择。
EN: Whether it's good or bad, this is my choice.

ZH: 不管你走不走，我都会等你。
EN: Whether you leave or not, I will wait for you.

ZH: 不管多忙，我一定会来参加你的婚礼。
EN: No matter how busy I am, I will definitely attend your wedding.

ZH: 不管你同不同意，这是我的最后决定。
EN: Whether you agree or not, this is my final decision.

ZH: 不管别人怎么说，我相信你。
EN: Regardless of what others say, I believe in you.

ZH: 不管我的家乡有多远，我都会永远怀念它。
EN: No matter how far away my hometown is, I will always cherish it.

ZH: 不管他多么有钱，他都无法买到幸福。
EN: No matter how rich he is, he cannot buy happiness.

ZH: 不管你是谁，我都愿意帮助你。
EN: I am willing to help you, whoever you are.

ZH: 不管这个项目有多复杂，我们都能做到。
EN: No matter how complex the project is, we can do it.

