EN: No matter how others view you, you must have confidence in yourself.

ZH: 不管成本多高，我们都要尽力完成这个工程。
EN: Regardless of the cost, we must make an effort to complete this project.

ZH: 不管我们相隔多远，我们的心总是靠近的。
EN: No matter how far apart we are, our hearts are always close.

ZH: 不管发生什么事，我都会一直支持你。
EN: No matter what happens, I will always support you.

ZH: 不管我们之间有多少障碍，我们都要克服它们。
EN: Regardless of the obstacles between us, we must overcome them.

ZH: 不管结果怎样，我们都会努力尝试。
EN: Regardless of the outcome, we will make an effort to try.

ZH: 不管别人怎么说，她永远是我最好的朋友。
EN: No matter what others say, she will always be my best friend.
